*shotgun-0.9.1 (04 Mar 2015)

  04 Mar 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +shotgun-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Add ruby22 target.

  09 Oct 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> shotgun-0.9-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby21 support.

  24 Apr 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> shotgun-0.9-r1.ebuild:
  Remove ruby18 support.

  11 Nov 2013; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -shotgun-0.9.ebuild:
  Cleanup old.

*shotgun-0.9-r1 (19 Oct 2013)

  19 Oct 2013; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> +shotgun-0.9-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby20 target.

  23 Sep 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> shotgun-0.9.ebuild:
  EAPI=4. Add ruby19.

  23 Sep 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -shotgun-0.8.ebuild:
  Cleanup.

*shotgun-0.9 (25 Feb 2011)

  25 Feb 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +shotgun-0.9.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  22 Jan 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -shotgun-0.6.ebuild,
  shotgun-0.8.ebuild:
  Relax rack dependency. Shotgun seems to work fine with rack 1.1.0 and rack
  1.2.1 installed.

  22 Jan 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -shotgun-0.6.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

